high_descs: Walk to the bed then turn left and walk to the desk then take a step to your right.
Pick up the clock on the shelf of the desk up high to the left of the desk.
Take a tiny step to your right.
Put the clock to the right of the mug.
Move slightly to the right.
Grab the other clock that's above the one we just set down.
Move slightly to your left.
Put the clock to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two clocks on the desk.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the desk.
Pick up the leftmost clock on the top shelf of the desk.
Back up a step from the desk while carrying the clock, but end still facing the desk.
Place the clock on the desk between the two white mugs.
Move closer to the desk, so you will be able to reach the other clock on the top shelf.
Pick up the other clock from the top shelf of the desk.
Back up a step from the desk while carrying the clock.
Place the second clock to the right of the first one previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two clocks to the main part of the desk.

high_descs: Move to the desk to the left of the bed
Pick up a clock from the desk
Move to the right side of the desk
Place the clock on the desk
Move to the desk to the left of the bed
Pick up a different clock from the desk
Move to the right side of the desk
Place the clock on the desk
anns.task_desc: Move two clocks on the desk to the same desk.
